<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="O" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Overgo" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Overgo</orth> (cf. <emph>O'ergo</emph>), to go beyond, to exceed: <cit><quote>a face that --es my blunt invention,</quote> <bibl n="shak. son 103.7" default="NO" valid="yes">Sonn. 103, 7</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>to o. thy plaints and drown thy cries,</quote> <bibl n="shak. r3 2.2.61" default="NO" valid="yes">R3 II, 2, 61</bibl></cit>.
